{
  "stem": "12343.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, some people was good, and some was bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even they was richer, some was good and some was bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They take advantage of the-- of the poor people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What way?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did they need some to work?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They take the poor people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, some time ago, the poor children [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called it the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Jewish, they call the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Here, they call it the-- I don't know how they call it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to go over there and-- and cry, why you send us for work?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] others, you think the others are gonna stay alive?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to hit them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Oh boy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was not no good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, experience, because they want to take me to work all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to work with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother said, no, you not going to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's my husband.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] They sent my-- my sister-- my sister to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said-- because if she goes, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're going to hit me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My sister always used to call for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's not-- [CRYING] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[CRYING] My sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[CRYING] She [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If I ever go, sometimes take away, you never come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even though I said, no, I want for him to go, she said no, he's not going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You should fight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] See, that's why I [? never ?] liked to act, said come like this still.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got too much trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[CRYING] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Then another thing with the Judenrat-- how call-- how you call the unit-- the [? committee, ?] [? committee ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They do something else, or they started to [INAUDIBLE] trouble.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then I work later on with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] never [? can sometimes ?] [? get on ?] not good.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
